{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#11691: when plain element with v-bind=\"obj\" has style property, style property mutation is not work",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:22:21.735527+00:00",
  "text": "when plain element with v-bind=\"obj\" has style property, style property mutation is not work\n\n### Vue version\n\nlatest 3.4.38\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nWhen click the button to change the style's color, The color of the template text is not changed\n\n### What is expected?\n\nHope the color of this template text can change normally\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nIt doent work. The template color is not changed\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
